msgid ""
"The due date %(invoice_date_due)s falls within the period "
"(%(range_overlap)s) of not pay to the partner.If, upon confirming the "
"invoice, the date mentioned does not meet the conditions, said date will be "
"changed to the first valid one."
msgstr ""
"La fecha de vencimiento %(invoice_date_due)s se encuentra dentro del período "
"(%(range_overlap)s) de no pago al socio. Si, al confirmar la factura, la "
"fecha mencionada no cumple con las condiciones, se cambiará a la primera fecha válida."

